        "data": "<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Added</h3>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">​<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38988\">LCD-38988</a><span> </span>- Batch of Updates for Logs Screen:</strong><span> batch of improvements include multi-line support, improved expand/collapse for easier log visualization, and better filters. Say goodbye to cluttered logs and hello to efficient troubleshooting!</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5rem 0px; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: #2a303e; font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2a303e; font-family: ' Source Sans Pro' , ' Source Serif Pro' , -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, ' Segoe UI' , Roboto, ' Helvetica Neue' , Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #0b5fff; text-decoration: none; background-color: transparent;\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-40608\">LCD-40608</a><span> </span>- Fixed Nginx compilation bug:<span> </span></strong>fixed issue in configuration that led to nginx not compiling when certain conditions were met. </li>\n</ul>"
